{"tid":1131711,"cid":34,"subCid":0,"title":"(台測)美國眾神 第1-2季","createTime":"2019-04-29T23:41:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-04T11:22:25.000Z","uid":29160,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"bd652ea1152be6f0472b4859ade3fa6f0faf252b","tid":1131711,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-29T23:41:02.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">播唔完下次播返</span><br />\n<a href=\"http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fparadiseangel.wixsite.com%2Fthanksyour%2Fabout1&d=exB9%2BbP5di4RF4u3Oz7pYpMi8MJ45PejcSMOUziyDL0%3D&h=aafe055c\" target=\"_blank\">http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 關ADBLOCK先睇到V台 順便開返個FLASHPLAYER<br />\n<a href=\"http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Flive.sk-knower.com%2Fuser%2Fthanksyour%3Flive%3Dvl&d=exB9%2BbP5di4RF4u3Oz7pYpMi8MJ45PejcSMOUziyDL0%3D&h=3cc148c5\" target=\"_blank\">http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有OKRU睇<br />\n<a href=\"https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.wixstatic.com%2Fmedia%2Fd8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg&d=exB9%2BbP5di4RF4u3Oz7pYpMi8MJ45PejcSMOUziyDL0%3D&h=51fa5358\" target=\"_blank\">https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg</a> &lt;GOOGLE睇唔到解決方法好似係 BY伯爵 <br />\n<img src=\"https://lekturaobowiazkowa.pl/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/American_Gods_CharacterArt_MrWednesday_Amazon.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Flekturaobowiazkowa.pl%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F05%2FAmerican_Gods_CharacterArt_MrWednesday_Amazon.jpg&h=b518c5c1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://kknews.cc/entertainment/8m5e58n.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fkknews.cc%2Fentertainment%2F8m5e58n.html&d=exB9%2BbP5di4RF4u3Oz7pYpMi8MJ45PejcSMOUziyDL0%3D&h=202e06b4\" target=\"_blank\">https://kknews.cc/entertainment/8m5e58n.html</a> <img src=\"https://www.dramaqueen.com.tw/features/20190220/002.html\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dramaqueen.com.tw%2Ffeatures%2F20190220%2F002.html&h=9808733b&s={SIZE}\" /> &lt;角色介紹<br />\n1.原著小說於2001年出版，先後被翻譯成30多種語言，在全球廣為流傳。故事描述一場即將到來的戰爭，對立的雙方是聖經故事和神話傳說中的「古代眾神」和代表新世界的「美國眾神」。<br />\n該劇描述在監牢中的男主角─影，等待著有天可以出獄，望向藍天，重回妻子、好友的懷抱。某天，一條消息到來，他可以提前兩天出獄，但卻是因為他的愛妻和好友同時車禍身亡，出獄後的他失去了一切，除了自由。從監獄釋放後，穿越美國大陸的旅行過程中的一系列奇遇。講述了他與生活在美國土地上的各種神祇相遇，由此引發了出許多精彩動人、奇詭絢麗的故事<br />\n<br />\n2.第二季自上季結尾半小時後開場，延續星期三先生在伊絲特的派對上，敲響新、舊神之間的戰爭後，世界先生正籌備對星期三先生的復仇計畫。與此同時，科技小子尋找著媒體女神。然而在舊神這邊，星期三先生繼續與影子同行，提交開戰提議給舊神們。蘿拉和瘋子史溫尼結伴，影子開始了解這個充滿神祇的怪異世界，並以一位信徒的身分開闢一條道路，但此路卻遠遠與順遂兩字天差地遠。<br />\n<br />\n不論新神、舊神或是祂們一路上遇見的人，在事情發展不如預期下，他們都會發現自己正踏上橫跨美國的旅程&mdash;所有人都注定要在伊利諾州的開羅，引爆一場決定勝負的高點<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Faddons.mozilla.org%2Fen-US%2Ffirefox%2Faddon%2Fghostery%2F&d=exB9%2BbP5di4RF4u3Oz7pYpMi8MJ45PejcSMOUziyDL0%3D&h=4f2f4850\" target=\"_blank\">https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchrome.google.com%2Fwebstore%2Fdetail%2Fghostery%2Fmlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij%3Fhl%3Dzh-TW&d=exB9%2BbP5di4RF4u3Oz7pYpMi8MJ45PejcSMOUziyDL0%3D&h=f91632ed\" target=\"_blank\">https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW</a><br />\n裝左睇V台就唔會見左上果舊野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bafe98ec51e7f129c16db63a6d58b5bcc53162de","tid":1131711,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":1,